WEBVTT

00:05.047 --> 00:07.132
<i>Henry Deaver is in town.</i>

00:07.132 --> 00:09.468
‐ So?
‐ Oh, please,

00:09.468 --> 00:12.012
Ms. Pre‐teen Voyeur 1991.

00:12.012 --> 00:14.473
<i>Apparently he’s a lawyer.</i>

00:14.473 --> 00:16.558
I wish I could help you find
your client, Mr. Deaver.

00:16.558 --> 00:18.435
I can’t very well
call up a ghost.

00:21.230 --> 00:24.691
‐ Got a condition.
‐ Forty gets you eight fives.

00:24.691 --> 00:26.485
<i>You know, the best cure</i>

00:26.485 --> 00:28.987
for social anxiety? Sunlight.

00:28.987 --> 00:30.656
Well, I don’t have
social anxiety.

00:30.656 --> 00:32.950
Right. Your...

00:32.950 --> 00:34.868
undiagnosed psychic affliction.

00:34.868 --> 00:37.162
<i>There are nerves in the brain,</i>

00:37.162 --> 00:38.872
<i>they’re called mirror neurons.</i>

00:38.872 --> 00:40.749
<i>And they’re responsible</i>
<i>for empathy.</i>

00:40.749 --> 00:43.794
‐ Are you high?
‐ What? No.

00:43.794 --> 00:46.004
<i>I take half a pill</i>
<i>once a day</i>

00:46.004 --> 00:49.258
just to muffle
other people’s noise.

00:49.258 --> 00:51.301
‐ You’re Henry Deaver, right?
‐ Excuse me?

00:51.301 --> 00:52.761
Beloved local preacher

00:52.761 --> 00:54.429
<i>opens his home and his heart</i>

00:54.429 --> 00:55.973
<i>to poor screw‐up orphan.</i>

00:55.973 --> 00:57.391
<i>You lure him out</i>
<i>to Castle Lake,</i>

00:57.391 --> 00:59.184
<i>push him off the rocks‐‐</i>

00:59.184 --> 01:01.562
bye‐bye, Pastor Deaver.

01:01.562 --> 01:04.438
He died at home,
not at the lake.

01:04.438 --> 01:07.359
<i>Six days into the search,</i>

01:07.359 --> 01:09.486
<i>authorities are increasingly</i>
<i>doubtful</i>

01:09.486 --> 01:12.322
<i>that the 11‐year‐old Deaver boy</i>
<i>will be found alive.</i>

01:12.322 --> 01:14.867
<i>His father, Matthew Deaver,</i>

01:14.867 --> 01:17.411
<i>local reverend</i>
<i>at Church of the Incarnation,</i>

01:17.411 --> 01:19.663
<i>is recovering from his injuries</i>
<i>at home</i>

01:19.663 --> 01:21.957
<i>and is in stable condition.</i>

01:21.957 --> 01:24.001
<i>With highs still</i>
<i>hovering around zero...</i>

